Perfect — got it loud and clear. We're aligned, and the tweak is straightforward and improves usability even more.

### Final Confirmed GUI Layout (Updated with Your Corrections)

```
Full-Screen Root (Control, anchors_full_rect, theme=bg3_theme.tres)
├── Main HSplitContainer (left ~20-25%, center ~55-60%, right ~20-25%)
│   ├── Left Panel (Category Navigation – Fixed width)
│   │   └── VBoxContainer
│   │       ├── Title Label ("Azgaar World Generator")
│   │       └── TabContainer (VERTICAL tabs – one per category)
│   │           ├── Terrain & Heightmap
│   │           ├── Climate & Environment
│   │           ├── Societies & Politics
│   │           ├── Settlements & Scale
│   │           └── (Future: Advanced / Visual)
│   ├── Center Panel (Map Display – Largest, expand_fill)
│   │   └── Azgaar WebView (GDCef – full embedded browser showing live Azgaar map)
│   │       (Future toggle: switch to mini 3D Terrain3D preview after bake)
│   └── Right Panel (Active Controls & Global Inputs – Dynamic population)
│       └── ScrollContainer (for long groups)
│           ├── Archetype Preset OptionButton (top – always visible)
│           ├── Seed Input (SpinBox – always visible, with randomize button)
│           ├── Section Title Label (e.g., "Terrain & Heightmap" – updates with selected tab)
│           ├── Parameter rows (only for currently selected category)
│           │   ├── templateInput (OptionButton)
│           │   ├── pointsInput (HSlider + value label)
│           │   ├── heightExponentInput (HSlider)
│           │   ├── allowErosion (CheckBox)
│           │   └── etc. (dynamically populated based on left tab)
│           ├── Separator / Spacer
│           └── (Tooltips, performance warning icons per control)
└── Bottom HBoxContainer (full wide, centered)
    ├── Generate with Azgaar Button (large, gold-accented)
    ├── Bake to 3D Button (disabled until complete)
    └── Status Label / Progress Bar (updates during generation)
```

### Why This Works Even Better
- **Left:** Pure navigation — clean, minimal, focused on categories only. No clutter.
- **Right:** Always shows the **global controls** (Archetype + Seed) at the top, then the **selected category's parameters** below. This keeps essential inputs always accessible without forcing the user to hunt for them.
- **Center:** Still the hero — the live map preview dominates the screen.
- **Flow remains intuitive:** Pick category on left → see/tweak its params on right → archetype/seed always handy on right → generate → watch center → bake.

### User Flow (Quick Recap with Changes)
1. Open World Builder → three-panel layout loads.
2. Select archetype preset (top of right panel) → all category parameters auto-populate (clamped by hardware).
3. Enter/customize seed (right panel, just below archetype).
4. Click a category tab on left → right panel updates to show only that group's controls.
5. Tweak parameters in right panel.
6. Hit "Generate with Azgaar" → options.json written → reload → center shows generation → polling detects completion.
7. Bake to 3D → center (future) toggles to 3D preview.

No other changes needed — this is clean, thematic, responsive, and fully matches your vision.

We're locked in. Ready to move forward?

